title: Here’s What New York Is Wearing to Fashion Week FW17
text:
Visit the original post to see all 23 images from this gallery. 
Location: New York, USA
Season: FW17
Key Looks: The polka dot puffer jacket bonanza in #5, those wacky half-and-half jeans in #7, our girl Sita murdering it in the all-MISBHV ensemble at #16.
For more street style action, check out our report from Raf Simons’ FW17 show at New York Fashion Week: Men’s.
